Between May and June 1993, Slovenia competed in the qualifiers for the
EuroBasket 1993
, where the team won all seven games and therefore qualified for its first
EuroBasket
. At the main tournament, held in Germany, Slovenia finished in 14th place out of 16 teams with one win and two defeats. Between May and June 1993, Slovenia competed in the qualifiers for the

Exporting a Protocol
Exporting a protocol saves it in a place of your choosing as a proprietary ","os_name":"V1.2","os_version":"os1.11","command_name":null,"command":"Protocol Repository and Exporting

Once protocols are created, they can be exported for use in other sciNote projects and/or copied directly to the sciNote Protocol Repository, where they are versioned and accessible to designated users.

Exporting a Protocol
